-- Note: Unless you save your query, these tabs will NOT persist if you clear your cookies or change browsers.

SELECT avg(s.total_amount::numeric ) as average_order
from postcard_company_core.fact_sales s

-- Note: Unless you save your query, these tabs will NOT persist if you clear your cookies or change browsers.

SELECT d.first_day_of_month , sum(s.total_amount) as totalamount  
from postcard_company_core.fact_sales s
join postcard_company_core.dim_date d on s.bought_date_key  = d.date_key 

group by d.first_day_of_month

-- Note: Unless you save your query, these tabs will NOT persist if you clear your cookies or change browsers.

SELECT  c.channel_name , d.first_day_of_month, sum(s.total_amount ) as total_sales
from postcard_company_core.fact_sales s
join postcard_company_core.dim_channel c on s.channel_key   = c.channel_key  
join postcard_company_core.dim_date d on d.date_key= s.bought_date_key
group by c.channel_name , d.first_day_of_month

-- Note: Unless you save your query, these tabs will NOT persist if you clear your cookies or change browsers.

SELECT  g.city_name  , d.day_of_week   , sum(s.qty::numeric) as total_qty
from postcard_company_core.fact_sales s
join postcard_company_core.dim_geography g on g.geography_key  = s.geography_key 
join postcard_company_core.dim_date d on d.date_key = s.bought_date_key 

group by g.city_name  , d.day_of_week

select reseller_name, bought_date_key/10000 as year, sum(commissionpaid::numeric) as comissionpaid 


from postcard_company_core.fact_sales s

join postcard_company_core.dim_salesagent  sa on sa.sales_agent_key = s.reseller_id

group by reseller_name, bought_date_key/10000

having sa.reseller_name <> 'Direct Sales'

-- Note: Unless you save your query, these tabs will NOT persist if you clear your cookies or change browsers.

SELECT g.country_name, sum(s.total_amount) as totalamount

from postcard_company_core.fact_sales s 
join postcard_company_core.dim_geography g on s.geography_key  = g.geography_key 

group by g.country_name
